greeting: Greetings from The On-Line Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences! http://oeis.org/

results.name: Triangle, read by rows, where T(n,k) = (k/n)*Sum_{d|n} A096800(d,k).
comment: Triangle A096800 lists row polynomials P_n(y), that satisfy the g.f.: A096651(x,y) = Product_{n>=1} 1/(1-x^n)^[P_n(y)/n], with P_n(0)=0 for n>=1; the row sums of A096651^n form the n-dimensional partitions.
results.author: _Paul D. Hanna_, Jul 13 2004
